column5:
(Diagnosis in progress, so take with a pinch of salt)

My thinking is: love is just brain juice and neurons firing. I guess it doesn’t make a SO less ‘special’ to you, but I think - as a social concept - there is far too much emphasis placed on love.

Yeah, I’ve had to self-refer to a service once before and it was pretty poor - they just pied me off, basically.

And cheers for signposting man - I’ll take a look.
You can light an oven to make the hideout safer during the night and you can also cook there in order to acquire new skills :)
